'''拉斐爾圖稿'''（'''Raphael Cartoons'''） 是7座大型掛氈，現存於倫敦[[維多利亞和阿爾伯特博物館|維多利亞和阿爾伯特博物館]]，由[[文藝復興|文藝復興]]畫家[[拉斐爾|拉斐爾]]在1515年至1516年完成。目前僅存的10幅畫是應[[教宗良十世|教宗良十世]]的請求而畫於[[宗座宮殿|宗座宮殿]][[西斯汀小堂|西斯汀小堂]]之內。<ref>[http://www.airiti.com/teps/ec_en/ecjnlarticleView.aspx?jnlcattype=1&jnlptype=1&jnltype=462&jnliid=13259&issueiid=137895&atliid=2598969 十八世紀英國「宗教藝術」重建的契機：從對拉斐爾圖稿及二則宗教圖像的論辯談起] 謝佳娟</ref><ref>[http://links.jstor.org/sici?sici=0004-3079%28195809%2940%3A3%3C193%3ARTATC%3E2.0.CO%3B2-Y&size=LARGE&origin=JSTOR-enlargePage JSTOR] ''Raphael's Tapestries and Their Cartoons'',John White, John Shearman, The Art Bulletin, Vol. 40, No. 3 (Sep., 1958), pp. 193-221. Rather oddly, both Jones & Penny and Grove Art say, wrongly, that the V&A have eight of the ten cartoons.</ref><ref>Quoted in Wölffin, Heinrich; ''Classic Art; An Introduction to the Renaissance'', p. 108, 1952 in English (1968 edition), Phaidon, New York.</ref>

